<db:section xml:id="normalizedRect-prop">
<db:title>normalizedRect : QRectF</db:title>
<db:para>Specifies the normalised rectangle for the viewport, i.e. the viewport rectangle is specified relative to the render surface size. Whole surface sized viewport is specified as [0.0, 0.0, 1.0, 1.0], which is the default.</db:para>
